                <p class='bold'>Housing Assignments</p>
                <p>
                   Apple contracts with several apartment complexes typically within 5 miles of your work location or within 3 miles from an Apple shuttle stop. You will be assigned a unit based on availability. Air conditioning and washer/dryer units are not available in all apartment units. Please work with the Apple program manager regarding any accommodation requests you may have. We reserve the right to reassign you to a different unit mid-internship if the need arises and when we need to consolidate back to long-term leases.
                </p>
            </div>

