                <p class='bold'>Estimated Commute from Intern Corporate Housing</p>
                <p>
                   Even though corporate housing may be less than 5 or 10 miles from your work location, interns with cars can still expect traffic delays in the Bay Area. Rush-hour traffic can be unpredictable and frustrating, so you should always try to leave early to anticipate any possible weather or traffic delays. Interns without cars who rely on public transportation and/or the Apple shuttle system can expect on average a 60-minute door-to-door commute when you factor in the walk to the closest shuttle stop, the shuttle commute, and the walk to your building.
                </p>
            </div>

