                <p class='bold'>Beds for Future Roommates or Housemates</p>
                <p>
                    Prior to each new roommate/housemate arrival, NCH will prepare the vacant bed with new linens, a laundry basket, towels, bath soaps, and a goody bag. These items should not be tampered with by anyone other than the new arriving intern. NCH will return prior to the new intern’s scheduled arrival to confirm the setup. A reset fee of US$150.00 will be equally divided and charged to the current intern residents if the vacant bed and items have been tampered with.
                </p>
            </div>


